914291,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b377f8f08c99d3dd512542634fda3da43f8cff6","tid":1914291,"uid":40979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T12:27:26.000Z","msg":"唔係唔再出入台證咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T12:28:47.000Z","msg":"出到入臺證<br />\n都係要隔離14日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T12:30:17.000Z","msg":"依家停哂所有網上申請同落地申請，隔幾多日都唔關香港人事"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T12:32:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.teco-hk.org/News_Content.aspx?n=D9D343F0F08E74FC&amp;sms=A673E23B4E4B5DEE&amp;s=6BE3B56B6D3B1F82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teco-hk.org%2FNews_Content.aspx%3Fn%3DD9D343F0F08E74FC%26sms%3DA673E23B4E4B5DEE%26s%3D6BE3B56B6D3B1F82&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuODT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=72785618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.teco-hk.org/News_Content.aspx?n=D9D343F0F08E74FC&amp;sms=A673E23B4E4B5DEE&amp;s=6BE3B56B6D3B1F82</a><br />\n針對香港網絡謠傳我政府將暫發港澳居民入臺證乙事之相關說明<br />\n發布日期：109-01-27<br />\n<br />\n                                                                                                           109年1月27日<br />\n陸委會表示，針對香港網絡謠傳我政府將於今日晚間十二時前暫發港澳居民入臺證乙事，絕非事實，在此特予澄清。鑑於新型冠狀病毒疫情擴散，對於持有港澳特區護照的香港永久居民若有計劃來臺，我們呼籲必須依我疾管署的相關規定，確實做好健康防護。倘有出現發燒、咳嗽等不適症狀，應戴上口罩儘速就醫，並告知醫師旅遊史、職業別等資訊。相關資訊可參閱疾管署網站或撥打免付費防疫專線1922（或0800-001922）洽詢。"},{"pid":"bc2addb8f65e65b6fc0e240bea04138cb421db7e","tid":1914291,"uid":40979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7c92bcda1a0f7259145e76b9e5222f0b069ad18","tid":1914291,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b245446f0f0f9fd2e35d07198e79b6c8fd7110c1","tid":1914291,"uid":40979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd31908ae70cd03e8e6a4103fc0bee4b5451cc76","tid":1914291,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T12:28:47.000Z","msg":"出到入臺證<br />\n都係要隔離14日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T12:30:17.000Z","msg":"依家停哂所有網上申請同落地申請，隔幾多日都唔關香港人事"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2